      <h2 id="t3">3. Regulatory Status</h2>
      <p>HNB Investment Bank Limited is a licensed investment bank regulated by the Securities and Exchange Commission of Sri Lanka (SEC) and the Central Bank of Sri Lanka (CBSL). Our subsidiaries hold the following licences:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>HNB Stockbrokers (Pvt) Ltd — CSE Trading Member Licence</li>
        <li>HNB Securities Ltd — Primary Dealer Licence (CBSL)</li>
        <li>Lanka Ventures Limited — Venture Capital Company (BOI approved)</li>
      </ul>

