        <li>You are acting on your own account unless we have specifically agreed otherwise</li>
      </ul>
      <p>The Company does not provide personalised investment advice unless specifically contracted to do so. Market commentary and research published on the Website are for informational purposes only.</p>

      <h2 id="t6">6. Execution of Orders</h2>
      <p>The Company will execute client orders in accordance with its Order Execution Policy and the rules of the relevant exchange or market. We shall not be liable for delays or failures in execution caused by market conditions, exchange system outages, or force majeure events. Settlement of securities transactions is subject to the rules of the CDS and CSE.</p>

