      <p>Fees, commissions, and charges applicable to our Services are set out in the relevant service agreement and fee schedule provided to you at account opening. We reserve the right to amend our fee schedule with 30 days' written notice. All quoted fees are exclusive of applicable taxes unless stated otherwise.</p>

